<paragraph blockId="9.[241,1073,1254,1408]" pageId="9" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[267,376,1360,1381]" pageId="9" pageNumber="134">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was described by Roelofs from 
<collectingCountry box="[863,923,1361,1382]" name="Japan" pageId="9" pageNumber="134">Japan</collectingCountry>
and has since been discovered in 
<collectingCountry box="[451,517,1387,1408]" name="China" pageId="9" pageNumber="134">China</collectingCountry>
. This represents a new distribution record.
</paragraph>
